{"tid":185824,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE]收音機問題","createTime":"2017-04-03T17:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T10:38:54.000Z","uid":425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f26ec282d32996cf41a20f8499a42523d8fd0e6","tid":185824,"uid":425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"想問下有無人用SONY S84<br />\n有個制係FM AM 同中間(MONO), 應該SET邊個?<br />\n同埋我發覺隻手一渣住部機就即刻明顯細聲勁多 係咪正常<br />\n另外有無人考果陣係左耳右耳一部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73a1591d6cb1ca26a507fe07d088799792af1ca","tid":185824,"uid":425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849c07a876b6a349f2f836234fc947def6ceed42","tid":185824,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"Mono <br />\n左一部右一部係試機果陣先會"},{"pid":"95512fc008ca0bfb34d2283d123f7dd4a1e716fb","tid":185824,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T01:29:02.000Z","msg":"Fm先岩 打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e5dedfc8ea99225b5b4944735ce9419a09a0d7","tid":185824,"uid":34805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T01:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mono <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">左一部右一部係試機果陣先會</span></blockquote><br />\n我個Fd上年考會咁<br />\n佢話就算其中一部突然冇聲都唔會miss"},{"pid":"6b3b357845c8a32a00b448961d801d84564efdbe","tid":185824,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span>"},{"pid":"fe500680a9ea95ac4ebe6de9a54f33b4e5e4d8bd","tid":185824,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span>"},{"pid":"910714c750ada572f84eeb545ce46ce04b0e299e","tid":185824,"uid":425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span></blockquote><br />\n佢會唔會check 兩圈果d 唔係咁舒服"},{"pid":"08d9e9ba1a8dfc869b1b3d1d70b2164eb69e0d31","tid":185824,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span></blockquote><br />\n佢會唔會check 兩圈果d 唔係咁舒服</blockquote><br />\n上年有收音機試場捉過earphone有咪/volume control <br />\n<br />\nInfrared receiver好似要用兩圈，用三圈聽唔到/無咁好( according to eaa)"},{"pid":"b6a527b3289693e1fd67de447ef571fad8b3e113","tid":185824,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span></blockquote><br />\n佢會唔會check 兩圈果d 唔係咁舒服</blockquote><br />\n上年有收音機試場捉過earphone有咪/volume control <span style=\"color: red;\">高登好似見過，唔sure</span><br />\n<br />\nInfrared receiver好似要用兩圈，用三圈聽唔到/無咁好( according to eaa)</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ccec1fd97649cd59a873ea27ca8b7a723ee015a4","tid":185824,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span></blockquote><br />\n佢會唔會check 兩圈果d 唔係咁舒服</blockquote><br />\n上年有收音機試場捉過earphone有咪/volume control <span style=\"color: red;\">高登好似見過，唔sure</span><br />\n<br />\nInfrared receiver好似要用兩圈，用三圈聽唔到/無咁好( according to eaa)</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n搵翻上年個post有人留言:<br />\n&quot;我想問 我今日帶錯iPhone有mic既耳機 <br />\n要去特別室 會唔會扣分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n<br />\n咁你都嚇一嚇啦，小心為上"},{"pid":"c0b089a45f9c38a420c57a280bf47520d562ee02","tid":185824,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160410/00176_030.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160410%2F00176_030.html&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7V5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=603b771f\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160410/00176_030.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年4月10日<br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試（DSE）語文聆聽科因有考生<strong>使用違規的連接麥克風手機耳筒</strong>，致不同試場出現「執法不一」情況，引發爭議！文憑試英文科卷三聆聽及綜合能力卷昨晨開考，部分考生直言，因試場內有太多考生帶備違規的手機耳筒被「捉到」，須被安排改到特別室應考，並致個別特別室「逼爆」；但亦有考生踢爆並非每間應試學校都捉，部分考生質疑監考員執法不一，或會製造不公。香港考試及評核局則指，考生若因使用違規耳筒，會被要求到特別室應考或記錄在試場報告，但<strong>不會被扣分</strong><br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢今年點做，一係當無事，一係大家一齊入特別室。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好搏啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"849f7f31ebe5979272cb679dc750336f5dbc9425","tid":185824,"uid":43979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span></blockquote><br />\n佢會唔會check 兩圈果d 唔係咁舒服</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n利申 考過5次dse"},{"pid":"950c18b770eaef33c2abb2573e009519a9249286","tid":185824,"uid":183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span></blockquote><br />\n佢會唔會check 兩圈果d 唔係咁舒服</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n利申 考過5次dse</blockquote><br />\n得鬼閒check咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1afdc4fdee60a52618279e3f62c084c2c1c965e","tid":185824,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過往幾年耳機既要求:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">耳筒的電線不可與任何麥克風或音量控制連接</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">infrared試場要帶只有兩個絕緣體(插頭得兩個線圈)既耳機</span></span></blockquote><br />\n佢會唔會check 兩圈果d 唔係咁舒服</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n利申 考過5次dse</blockquote><br />\n得鬼閒check咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好少話唔比<br />\n但有耳機個啲駁落去係有機會出唔到聲<br />\n所以先要用返兩圈"},{"pid":"411279d951f7131080ff769517a31ab2585c7143","tid":185824,"uid":5480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"有mic都唔用得？"},{"pid":"1ab59c2d94dd645ed13c56c7152768d4be0017da","tid":185824,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有mic都唔用得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔得架<br />\n因為驚你部機識得錄音"},{"pid":"8495748846fb50928938d17bfe41a92ec368cfde","tid":185824,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"用左有mic會點？<br />\n聽日想去舉報人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672fe782445fe2367c6af1bf0af3c63650ee3d1e","tid":185824,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"見過人用iphone耳機都冇事 不過最好唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}